      <p><strong class="font-semibold">Fair Use Notice:</strong> This Site may contain copyrighted material the use of which has not always been specifically authorized by the copyright owner. We make such material available in our efforts to advance understanding of environmental, political, human rights, economic, democracy, scientific, and social justice issues, etc., believing this constitutes a 'fair use' of any such copyrighted material as provided for in relevant copyright law. If you wish to use copyrighted material from this site for purposes of your own that go beyond 'fair use', you must obtain permission from the copyright owner.</p>

      <p><strong class="font-semibold">No Endorsement:</strong> Reference to any specific commercial product, process, or service by trade name, trademark, manufacturer, or otherwise, does not necessarily constitute or imply its endorsement, recommendation, or favoring by {siteName}.</p>

      <p><strong class="font-semibold">Limitation of Liability:</strong> Under no circumstance shall we have any liability to you for any loss or damage of any kind incurred as a result of the use of the site or reliance on any information provided on the site. Your use of the site and your reliance on any information on the site is solely at your own risk.</p>

      <p><strong class="font-semibold">Changes to Disclaimer:</strong> We reserve the right to make changes to this Disclaimer at any time and for any reason. We will alert you about any changes by updating the "Last Updated" date of this Disclaimer.</p>

      <p><strong class="font-semibold">Contact Us:</strong> If you have any questions about this Disclaimer, please contact us via {contactMethod}.</p>

